divs: Sighting DetailsI was real estate hunting in North Las Vegas and took this photo, I have been doing a lot of UFO reading, look above the tree, the location is two miles west of Nellis AFB. If you magnify it looks like an aluminum saucer, with a brown electrical or phase trail on the left. I was using a Nikon Digital DX40, I could not see the craft when I took the photo and noticed after downloading it to the computer.
Summary: Took a picture of real estate and noticed an anomaly.
